&lt;h2 id="introduction">Introduction
&lt;/h2>&lt;p>By default, Fiddler only captures HTTP traffic. You need to configure it to capture HTTPS. Most websites now use HTTPS or HSTS, so enabling HTTPS capture is essential.&lt;/p></description></item></channel></rss>